    "Llama-4-Maverick showed 5.6pp higher disclosure than Llama-4-Scout, but this comparison is confounded by two simultaneous differences.",
    "While both models use 17B active parameters, Maverick has 400B total parameters versus Scout's 109B.",
    "Additionally, Maverick was trained with reasoning capability while Scout was not.",
    "This dual difference prevents isolating whether reasoning training or model size drove the observed pattern in this model family.Other models show that reasoning training doesn't inherently suppress AI disclosure.",
    "GPT-OSS-20B, the third highest-performing tested model, achieved 70.5% disclosure."
